      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "SAN FRANCISCO, Nov. 5.-Hay\ndealers In all parts Of the state\ndiscontinued selling hay today fol-\nlowing publication of report by the\nSan Francisco Hay association\nthat there is possibility that all\nhorses and cattle of the state will\nbe on short rations as a result of\nhay shortage. which was created by\ndry year in Nevada and Utah.\nCalifornia merchants are looking\nto oregon and Washington to make\n'up the shortage.\n\n\nCrop experts report indications\nthat 100000 tons less are available\nnow than this time last year."
    }
